Elevator Service Technician (Brisbane Based)

Eletech – Kelvin Grove QLD

$57 - $65 an hour Full time

25d ago, from seek.com.au

Apply on company site

Company

Eletech Pty Ltd

Position available: Lift Service Technician

Be prepared to join a company with a positive work culture and attitude of success. Eletech prides itself on being a leader in elevator installation, service, maintenance and repair.

*Competitive industry wage

*Dual cab vehicle provided

Duties and Responsibilities

- Complete scheduled services, repairs and call out (breakdown) visits effectively and efficiently;

- Participate in After Hours On-Call Roster (approx 1 week in 5 on-call);

Duties and Responsibilities

- Complete scheduled services, repairs and call out (breakdown) visits effectively and efficiently;
- Participate in After Hours On-Call Roster (approx 1 week in 5 on-call);
- Effectively plan workload, in conjunction with team of service technicians;
- Be a good communicator and maintain excellent customer relations;
- Ensure all work is carried out in line with company WH&S policy and procedures;
- Works within quality standards and procedures;
- Ensure true and accurate reports of activities and work carried out;
- Present a strong customer focus.
- Ensure that Company Vehicle is maintained in accordance with manufacturers schedule and company policies.
- Supervise and train apprentices as and when required (Eletech is committed to training and development of apprentices).

Education and Qualifications Required

- Queensland or other Australian equivalent Electrical fitter/mechanic license;
- Manual Driver's License;
- Construction White Card.

Experience

- Experience in the lift industry preferred;
- Electrical licence required;
- Familiarity with PLC and VF Drives;
- Mechanical experience and competence.

- Experience in the industry preferred;

- Electrical licence required;

- Familiarity with PLC and VF Drives;

- Mechanical experience and competence.

Requirements:

Candidates will be required to obtain a National Police Certificate and Working with Children Check in the course of their employment.

Candidates will be required to be flu-vaccinated due to Eletech's customer's requirements (Health Care and Aged Care facilities).

*This position is based in Brisbane but can include travel to all areas in South East QLD. Successful applicant will be flexible and self motivated, working within a team environment.

